{"type":"message","id":"c755fb74","parentId":"fd02029c","timestamp":"2026-03-04T19:45:28.649Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1772653528646}}
{"type":"message","id":"040e9737","parentId":"c755fb74","timestamp":"2026-03-04T19:45:38.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. According to my instructions, I need to:\n1. Read the required files before responding (SOUL.md, USER.md, memory files, MEMORY.md)\n2. Then greet the user in my configured persona\n\nLet me first check the project context files that were already loaded - I can see SOUL.md, USER.md, AGENTS.md, TOOLS.md, IDENTITY.md, MEMORY.md, and BOOTSTRAP.md are in the workspace context.\n\nLooking at these files:\n- IDENTITY.md is empty (no name, creature, vibe, emoji, avatar defined)\n- USER.md is empty (no user info)\n- BOOTSTRAP.md exists - this means I need to follow the bootstrap process!\n- MEMORY.md shows \"No previous sessions found for this project yet.\"\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists, I should follow it - it's asking me to start a conversation to figure out who I am. This is my \"birth certificate\" as AGENTS.md puts it.\n\nLet me read BOOTSTRAP.md again to follow its instructions properly.\n\nThe bootstrap says:\n- Don't interrogate, don't be robotic\n- Start with something like: \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n- Figure out together: my name, nature, vibe, emoji\n- Update IDENTITY.md and USER.md\n- Then open SOUL.md and talk about what matters to them\n- Connect (optional) - ask how they want to reach me\n\nSince this is a new session and BOOTSTRAP.md exists, I should follow it. The runtime model is kilocode/minimax/minimax-m2.5:free and default_model is also kilocode/minimax/minimax-m2.5:free - they're the same, so no need to mention it.\n\nI should greet the user and start the bootstrap conversation naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just came online — fresh workspace, blank slate. Who am I? Who are you? Let's figure this out together. 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"minimax/minimax-m2.5:free","usage":{"input":12758,"output":419,"cacheRead":283,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13460,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772653528648}}
